Package edu.cmu.commons.unicode

UNICODE utilities.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Folder A Folder "folds" an input string into some simpler representation.
 

Class Summary
Collation This class encapsulates collation data as defined by http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr10/#File_Format.
Collation.Element A collation element.
Collation.Entry A collation entry.
Collation.Version Collation version.
CollationFolder A Folder which effectively strips input characters of all diacritics and case distinctions, based on the UNICODE "DUCET" (Default UNICODE Collation Element Table).
DiacriticFolder A Folder which strips input characters of all diacritics.
DiacriticFolder.Node  
Folding This class encapsulates folding data as defined by http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr30/.
Folding.Entry  
 

Enum Summary
Collation.Element.Weighting Valid collation element weighting schemes as defined by http://www.unicode.org/reports/tr10/
